{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"POP3","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/POP","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>POP3</strong> (郵局協定)是一種常見協定(<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Protocol\">protocol</a>) 用於從伺服器接收郵件通過 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/TCP\">TCP <small>(en-US)</small></a> 鏈接.不同於<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/IMAP\">IMAP4 <small>(en-US)</small></a>, 由於 POP3 結構更爲複雜，更難以實施，POP3 不支持多資料夾。</p>\n<p>客戶端通常會從伺服器取回所有的訊息然後刪除伺服器上的訊息，但是 POP3 允許伺服器保留副本。目前幾乎所有的郵件伺服器和客戶端都支持 POP3.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"http://www.faqs.org/rfcs/rfc1939.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 1939</a> (POP3 的規範)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://www.faqs.org/rfcs/rfc2449.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 2449</a> (POP3 的規範擴展機制)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://www.faqs.org/rfcs/rfc1734.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 1734</a> (POP3 的規範認證機制)</li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/IMAP\">IMAP4 <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li>維基百科上的<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Post_Office_Protocol\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">POP</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"POP3 (郵局協定)是一種常見協定(protocol) 用於從伺服器接收郵件通過 TCP (en-US) 鏈接.不同於IMAP4 (en-US), 由於 POP3 結構更爲複雜，更難以實施，POP3 不支持多資料夾。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"POP3","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"POP3","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"POP3","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"POP3","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"z